        <body>
          <h1>RingCentral call and meeting recordings analytics</h1>
          <div>
          <p>
            This demo Web application allows you access your RingCentral account, read call recordings and meeting recordings. The audio content
            will be transcribed then the transcript will be saved to a local database together with the call or meeting metadata such as the date, the caller's
            and the callee's numbers.</br>
          </p>
          <p>
            Call and meeting recordings transcript will be analyzed and transformed from an unstructured content into a structured data using RingCentral AI for data analitics.
          </p>
          </p>
            Demo main features:
          </p>
            <ol>
              <li>Transcribe speech-to-text from call recordings and voicemail</li>
              <li>Allow users to search for a word or phrase from calls' transcripts.</li>
              <li>Allow users to search for calls from keywords, from number, to number.</li>
              <li>Play an audio content with stylish synchronized transcript.</li>
              <li>Enable users to interact with the audio content from the transcript by clicking on any word from the text to fast-forward or fast-backward to the selected word.</li>
              <li>Enable instant search for a word from the transcript and fast-forward to that spoken word in the audio content</li>
              <li>Extract actionable items from the speech.</li>
            </ol>
            <p>
            Technologies:
            <ul>
              <li>RingCentral Platform</li>
              <li>RingCentral AI</li>
          </ul>
            </p>
          </div>
